        experienceNote: "Lawyer and Legal Counsel Omar Al-Baghdadi's three decades of Saudi corporate practice include rare company formation nullity proceedings that require specialist constitutional expertise — giving Qanoni clients a decisive advantage in these technically demanding cases.",
